Email Spam Detection

Description

This project is a machine learning-based email spam detection system developed using Python. The model analyzes email content and classifies messages as spam or not spam.

Features

- Detects spam emails automatically
- Classifies emails as spam or legitimate
- Uses machine learning techniques for prediction
- Processes and analyzes email data

Technologies Used

- Python
- Machine Learning
- Data Analysis

Output

The system predicts whether an email is spam or not spam based on the input data.

